data.description: Tucked away in the heart of Lake Linganore in the Eaglehead Summerfield neighborhood, this 3 bedroom 3.5 bath townhome is ready for you!  Brand new paint throughout and new carpet/laminate on upper and lower levels.  Newer hvac, Stainless steel refrigerator.  All bedrooms have vaulted ceilings, primary has multiple closets/storage.  Fully fenced rear yard with deck and stone patio.  5 minute walk on path to Elementary School and tot lot, bball courts, and pool.  Daycare center located in neighborhood, 10 minutes to 70.  The neighborhood boasts multiple pools, walking/jogging, a dog park, paths, parks/playgrounds, and lake access at the beach.  Award winning Oakdale school district.
